{"tid":1947239,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★思捷6家歐洲附屬公司申請破產保護","createTime":"2020-03-28T07:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T10:23:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"70997f8c7585dbf3672e38204b10aacd19dda29a","tid":1947239,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:03:38.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200327/photo/bkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001_01p.jpg?20200328060439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20200328060439&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq3d5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=a6315fb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200327/photo/bkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001_01p.jpg?20200328060439</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n思捷環球(00330)公布，旗下歐洲附屬公司在新冠肺炎疫情以及各國政府的公眾衛生措施和嚴厲行動下，銷售情況進一步嚴重惡化，為保障集團，尤其歐洲附屬公司償付能力和資金流動性，業務仍能持續運作，集團根據德國破產法例，將6家附屬公司申請啟動財產保護訴訟程序，即是自行管理重組程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200327/bkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200327%2Fbkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001.html&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq3d5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=86cc9feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200327/bkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2eca049e4f7be140d42fcd0cdd90297fc072ed6e","tid":1947239,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200327/photo/bkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001_01b.jpg?20200328060439\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200327230019611-0327_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20200328060439&h=91d3a389&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0444475612226aaf484187219b24591584e4aecf","tid":1947239,"uid":54511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又破產 又保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明"},{"pid":"d80d261f08ec7072cc42da911ca0e6f183e9b63c","tid":1947239,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"屍捷人頭"},{"pid":"641802e49ff9bae6b9c892eb7abb45b59372087f","tid":1947239,"uid":324041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"一於轉型生產醫療用品啦！話唔定可以殺出條血路出嚟呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2204b46ba842587b3b67f684d7506b15b5614f1","tid":1947239,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"641802e49ff9bae6b9c892eb7abb45b59372087f","tid":1947239,"uid":324041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"一於轉型生產醫療用品啦！話唔定可以殺出條血路出嚟呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd66bcef74b8591031b76444fb2087ff0ca47c4","tid":1947239,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"1蚊私有化"},{"pid":"8e071b1caae49fe49515adfe2fb39cf8442184a7","tid":1947239,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"經營ESPRIT的思捷環球（330）早前再公佈新的重組大計，公司今日舉行股東會。有小股東「做足功課」，準備好同業數據與ESPRIT比較，質疑管理層多年來無心戀戰，「迷惘咗8、9年」，並不看好是次重組計劃。<br />\n<br />\n大會投票過後，場內約有50多名小股東拿過禮物，仍留守會場，質問管理層。<br />\n<br />\n有小股東準備好快速時裝品牌Zara、H&amp;M及本地服裝股佐丹奴（709）的業績與ESPRIT比較，他指，公司自2009年宣佈從華潤手中購入思捷中國已是不智的決定，此後業務一直走下坡，經歷供股等「乜嘢財技都出齊」，但仍然「迷惘咗8、9年，搵唔到出路」。<br />\n<br />\n他又憶述，ESPRIT在興發街的黃金時代，當時只有佐丹奴和ESPRIT兩大休閒服裝界龍頭，但兩公司至今業績高下立見，「人哋佐丹奴最衰嘅時候有個幾（意指股價），之後升返上5個幾，今年就3個幾；我哋（ESPRIT)呢，唔好講百幾嗰啲，無謂講，而家淨返個幾！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，該名股東對新任行政總裁Anders Kristiansen甚是欣賞，皆因Kristiansen在會上介紹自己正身穿ESPRIT的西裝褸，該股東手伸拇指說：「佢(CEO)好夠膽，我要畀個like佢！」，此時用手指向一眾管理層說：「有幾多個着緊你哋公司嘅衫？個個鍾意你份人工，但又唔鍾意你份工！」場內惹來一陣笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n另一名小股東質疑公司不懂中國時裝市場情況。該名小股東說，ESPRIT以質料好見稱，「但佢哋（中國市場）唔係要呢啲呀！佢哋最好要爛得快啲嘅（質料），等佢哋可以換得多啲，價錢要啱佢哋。」<br />\n<br />\n執行主席柯清輝隨即向股東們介紹坐在台下的中國設計師，他重申，公司重視亞洲市場，往後銷往亞洲或中國的產品中，將有30%在中國設計，公司亦有設計師長駐上海。<br />\n<br />\n他坦言，公司曾掙扎過是否應走快速時裝之路，但認為轉型行不通，ESPRIT的忠實顧客喜愛品牌的質量，而且品牌多年來最成功的是批發業務，走向快速時裝與批發生意難以並存。<br />\n<br />\n柯清輝在會後會見傳媒時重申，公司今後會聆聽顧客的需求，被問到多年來業績無起色有否想過賣盤，又有沒有人曾經接洽，他即擰頭說：「冇！如果唔係點會有新總裁又有新計劃啫？」"},{"pid":"af07eb133bbb9edbca54038778f7b70226b608af","tid":1947239,"uid":11388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"原來淨返7毫6⋯⋯⋯⋯市值係07年百份之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7912fe50ddab06c7cd7a5688221515f561442c72","tid":1947239,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"等睇有人開post $133入點部署"},{"pid":"76b08f93ebf1a2c338a8c1795ed44293e904b929","tid":1947239,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b79859256566a2f6ebf8f892a0cb7ac0a1372d44","tid":1947239,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"af07eb133bbb9edbca54038778f7b70226b608af","tid":1947239,"uid":11388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"原來淨返7毫6⋯⋯⋯⋯市值係07年百份之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi